# Resolved Errors Archive
# Grants Training Suite V2 - Module Development

## Purpose
This file archives all resolved errors for reference and learning purposes.

## Error Archive Format
# ================================================================================
# Timestamp: YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS
# Phase: [Phase Name]
# Step: [Step Name]
# Error Type: [Error Category]
# Error Message: [Original error message]
# Context: [Context when error occurred]
# Root Cause: [Analysis of root cause]
# Solution: [How error was resolved]
# Resolution Date: YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS
# Prevention: [Prevention measures implemented]
# ================================================================================

## Archive Categories
# - Installation Errors (Phase 1)
# - Model Errors (Phase 2)
# - View Errors (Phase 3)
# - Security Errors (All Phases)
# - Performance Errors (All Phases)

## Archive Process
# 1. Move resolved errors from active error logs
# 2. Add resolution date and prevention measures
# 3. Categorize by phase and error type
# 4. Maintain chronological order
# 5. Use for future reference and learning

## Learning from Resolved Errors
# - Identify common error patterns
# - Improve development processes
# - Update error prevention strategies
# - Share knowledge with team
# - Create troubleshooting guides

